            <p class="comment-content">传习录后还有一辑阳明子序朱子晚年语录，称为《朱子晚年定论》。同心一德，体圣不二。公道公心，如日月行。象山默然良久，曰：“天地间没有个朱元晦，亦没有个陆子静。”此之谓也。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="796525134">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-796525134" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-796525134" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="796525134">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bcbulang/">边城不浪</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-04-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">心学两位大佬不仅讲学，还能做事。探求本心才能由狂入圣，有分教：仰首攀南斗，翻身倚北辰，举头天外望，无我这般人。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="653867283">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-653867283" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-653867283" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="653867283">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/69577160/">文海阁主</a>
                    <span>2013-03-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">致良知</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
